local plr = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer local Char = plr.Character
local HUM = Char:FindFirstChildWhichIsA("Humanoid")
local HRP = Char:WaitForChild("HumanoidRootPart") local RootJoint = HRP:FindFirstChild("RootJoint") local Original = RootJoint.C0
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService") local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService")
local TI = TweenInfo.new( 0.9, Enum.EasingStyle.Back )
RunService.Heartbeat:Connect(function(Time) if HRP:IsA("BasePart") then local Direct = HRP.CFrame:VectorToObjectSpace(HUM.MoveDirection) local Vel = HRP.CFrame:VectorToObjectSpace(HRP.AssemblyLinearVelocity)*0.1 Vel = Vector3.new( math.clamp(math.abs(Vel.X), .2, .2), 0, math.clamp(math.abs(Vel.Z), .2, .2) )
local X = Direct.X * Vel.X local Z = Direct.Z * Vel.Z
if Z < 0 then Z = 0 end
--RootJoint.C0 = RootJoint.C0:Lerp(Original*CFrame.Angles(unpack(Angle)),Time * 16) TweenService:Create(RootJoint,TI,{C0 = Original * CFrame.Angles(-Z,-X,0)}):Play() end end)
